question: Where can I find fast food restaurant in the direction of SEA LIFE Minnesota Aquarium, Bloomington, MN within 110 kilometers from Moberg Park, MN?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-92.890556 45.372778)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-93.240076 44.854752)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-92.890556 45.372778)',4326)::geography, 110000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-92.890556 45.372778)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
